{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01W4gk9dRjRckyVx9iMwxC4r","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Harness Cost Report\n     2→\n     3→Total API-equivalent cost: $862.24\n     4→Total API calls: 6281\n     5→Average cost per story: $4.05 (158 stories)\n     6→\n     7→## Cost by Token Type\n     8→\n     9→| Type | Tokens | Rate | Cost | % |\n    10→|------|--------|------|------|---|\n    11→| Cache reads | 335,507,660 | $1.50/MTok | $503.26 | 58% |\n    12→| Cache writes | 11,963,064 | $18.75/MTok | $224.31 | 26% |\n    13→| Output | 1,792,734 | $75/MTok | $134.46 | 16% |\n    14→| Input | 14,666 | $15/MTok | $0.22 | 0% |\n    15→\n    16→## Cost by Phase\n    17→\n    18→| Phase | Calls | Cost | % |\n    19→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    20→| verify | 3678 | $459.37 | 53.3% |\n    21→| orchestrator | 866 | $191.08 | 22.2% |\n    22→| retro | 743 | $101.67 | 11.8% |\n    23→| code-review | 375 | $43.01 | 5.0% |\n    24→| create-story | 348 | $37.05 | 4.3% |\n    25→| dev-story | 271 | $30.07 | 3.5% |\n    26→\n    27→## Cost by Tool\n    28→\n    29→| Tool | Calls | Cost | % |\n    30→|------|-------|------|---|\n    31→| Bash | 2315 | $284.64 | 33.0% |\n    32→| Read | 1322 | $183.25 | 21.3% |\n    33→| Edit | 989 | $127.74 | 14.8% |\n    34→| Agent | 601 | $78.54 | 9.1% |\n    35→| Skill | 213 | $73.37 | 8.5% |\n    36→| Grep | 436 | $49.53 | 5.7% |\n    37→| Write | 155 | $27.61 | 3.2% |\n    38→| Glob | 107 | $18.82 | 2.2% |\n    39→| TodoWrite | 111 | $15.24 | 1.8% |\n    40→| ToolSearch | 28 | $3.10 | 0.4% |\n    41→\n    42→## Top 10 Most Expensive Stories\n    43→\n    44→| Story | Calls | Cost | % |\n    45→|-------|-------|------|---|\n    46→| unknown | 1118 | $223.10 | 25.9% |\n    47→| 16-5-rewrite-harness-run-verification-dispatch | 648 | $78.78 | 9.1% |\n    48→| 1-1-foo | 198 | $24.35 | 2.8% |\n    49→| 14-5-stack-aware-verify-dockerfile | 190 | $23.63 | 2.7% |\n    50→| 14-4-observability-backend-choice | 192 | $22.13 | 2.6% |\n    51→| 8-9-semgrep-rules-rust-observability | 121 | $17.10 | 2.0% |\n    52→| 16-7-update-knowledge-and-enforcement-docs | 108 | $13.54 | 1.6% |\n    53→| 8-2-expand-state-types-for-rust | 84 | $12.67 | 1.5% |\n    54→| 16-8-update-all-tests | 103 | $12.26 | 1.4% |\n    55→| 9-5-multi-stack-docs-remaining-consumers | 84 | $11.07 | 1.3% |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01BUkhT1jT2JjxkyFUssHPi8","session_id":"dd89eeb6-4b36-471f-9921-5a2de5e0ed08","uuid":"495e9699-d9bb-4231-80eb-3940122a87db","timestamp":"2026-03-28T12:12:38.847Z"}
