{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01NmsivxbqaLR9TkQQ8H9Tfm","type":"tool_result","content":"  4080→| Priority | Action | Status |\n  4081→|----------|--------|--------|\n  4082→| **P0** | Sprint is done. No more execution needed. | **DONE** |\n  4083→| **P1** | Make proof + state transition atomic (or state-first) | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4084→| **P1** | Attribute the \"unknown\" cost bucket ($222.57, 25.9%) | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4085→| **P1** | Add sprint-complete exit condition to Ralph's main loop | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4086→| **P1** | Verify state-reconciliation (story 11-3) fires on session start and actually reconciles | NEW |\n  4087→| **P2** | Optimize verification phase cost (53.3% of total, 15:1 ratio vs dev) | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4088→| **P2** | Add subagent guideline: capture test output once, grep from capture | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4089→| **P2** | Add bash version check or shellcheck enforcement for ralph scripts | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4090→| **P3** | Clean up legacy terms (black.box references) in patches/templates | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4091→| **P3** | Clean up `1-1-foo` phantom story references from tracking data | CARRY FORWARD |\n  4092→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01BUkhT1jT2JjxkyFUssHPi8","session_id":"dd89eeb6-4b36-471f-9921-5a2de5e0ed08","uuid":"7697cf1c-8d31-41b5-95cb-5a96130d62c3","timestamp":"2026-03-28T12:12:50.591Z"}
